text: Colobothea emarginata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Olivier in 1795. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Colobothea emarginata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1795
title: Colobothea emarginata
